snippet.title: Hidden Dogs: In the Dog House
snippet.description:
Hidden Dogs: In the Dog House is a hidden object game where you'll explore an English village to find your hidden friends.
Find dogs, items and mutts to earn keys, then use those keys to unlock new levels!
Help Labby convince his friends; Rolo, Weenie, Biff and Shep, to aid him in his quest to make a dog themed video game.

Go wishlist now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3363810/Hidden_Dogs_In_the_Dog_House/?beta=0

#indiegame #steamdemo #indiedev #gaming 

Publisher: Rhino Rock Studios
Developer: Admiral Egg Games
